			"offsets": {
				"from": 437940,
				"to": 440940
			},
			"text": "访客也是一样 反馈也是一样"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:20,940",
				"to": "00:07:24,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 440940,
				"to": 444940
			},
			"text": "你按照这个维度一个一个的拆解它的原因"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:24,940",
				"to": "00:07:25,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 444940,
				"to": 445940
			},
			"text": "拆解它的原因"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:25,940",
				"to": "00:07:28,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 445940,
				"to": 448940
			},
			"text": "然后再对里面的原因进行一个分析优化"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:28,940",
				"to": "00:07:30,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 448940,
				"to": 450940
			},
			"text": "就可以解决这个问题了"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:30,940",
				"to": "00:07:34,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 450940,
				"to": 454940
			},
			"text": "所以我们在优化的时候都是非常细致又微的"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:34,940",
				"to": "00:07:36,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 454940,
				"to": 456940
			},
			"text": "第二个就是自然流量占比"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
